casebody.data:
(March 17, 1954.)

(Republished.)

Delancey Kosher Restaurant & Caterers Corp., Appellant-Respondent, v. Phil Gluckstern et al., Respondents-Appellants, et al., Defendants.

Order denying defendants’ motion unanimously affirmed. Order entered on plaintiff’s motion unanimously modified in accordance with the opinion herein and, as so modified, affirmed, with $20 costs and disbursements to the appellant-respondent Delancey Kosher Restaurant & Caterers Corp. Opinion Per Curiam. Settle orders on notice. Present — Peek, P. J., Dore, Breitel, Bastow and Bergan, JJ. [See ante, p. 776; post, p. 944.]
